data.description: Welcome to 5335 Pine Street, Philadelphia, PA 19143 in the Walnut Hill community, This property has been beautifully & professionally remodeled and designed just for you. Upon entering the home from the front porch you walk into a bright and very spacious open floor plan that is designed for contemporary living with lots of natural light. The spacious kitchen with Stainless-Steel Appliances (Stove/Range and Dishwasher) also leads out to a rear yard where you can entertain or relax. This 4 bedroom, 1 bath home is conveniently located near the Farmers' market, Dog Park, many shops, cafes, and restaurants. Close to Penn, Drexel, University of the Sciences. 12 minutes to Rittenhouse Square by car or bike and plenty of convenient SEPTA options With convenient access to Center City, Philadelphia International Airport and all major highways. Welcome Home!!!!!!!!! Property is ready to show!
